descriptionHtml:
A quick retexture I made of the High Elves\' green eyes. All I did was to change the iris to have a somewhat pine-green tone, which kinda suits my liking better.

Edit 23/11/11: I now consider this replacer obsolete, since people now have released high resolution eye packs that looks alot better ingame respectively. One of them are \"Dorkdivas elf eye pack\", another one \"Ghogiels EYES replacer\". So I\'m just gonna leave this one for players who would like to stick with low res textures (which I think few will.)


Edit 1/2/2013: Added a highres eye texture that I\'ve been using for a while. I don\'t remember who originally made this eye texture which I altered and made greener. Feel free to give me a heads up what eye pack it\'s from.

Just extract the content into your data folder.
author: T3alrose
